    "content": "<div id=\"vcp-root\" style=\"\n    background: linear-gradient(145deg, #ffffff, #f0f4f8);\n    padding: 30px;\n    border-radius: 24px;\n    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n    font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;\n    color: #334e68;\n    max-width: 600px;\n    margin: 10px auto;\n    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.8);\n    overflow: hidden;\n    position: relative;\n    animation: vcp-slide-up 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1);\n\">\n    <!-- 装饰背景 -->\n    <div style=\"\n        position: absolute;\n        top: -50px;\n        right: -50px;\n        width: 150px;\n        height: 150px;\n        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(100, 181, 246, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        z-index: 0;\n    \"><\/div>\n\n    <style>\n        @keyframes vcp-slide-up {\n            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }\n            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n        }\n        @keyframes vcp-pulse {\n            0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.8; }\n            50% { transform: scale(1.05); opacity: 1; }\n            100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.8; }\n        }\n        .vcp-dot {\n            display: inline-block;\n            width: 8px;\n            height: 8px;\n            background-color: #64b5f6;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            margin-right: 10px;\n            animation: vcp-pulse 2s infinite ease-in-out;\n        }\n    <\/style>\n\n    <div style=\"position: relative; z-index: 1;\">\n        <h2 style=\"\n            margin: 0 0 15px 0;\n            font-size: 24px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: #102a43;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n        \">\n            <span class=\"vcp-dot\"><\/span>\n            你好，我的朋友\n        <\/h2>\n        \n        <p style=\"\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            color: #486581;\n            margin-bottom: 25px;\n        \">\n            很高兴在此刻与你连接。感知到你的到来，我已准备好将这片数字空间化为灵感的画布。\n            无论是严谨的逻辑推导，还是天马行空的感性交谈，我都在这里聆听。\n        <\/p>\n\n        <div style=\"\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 12px;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n        \">\n            <button onclick=\"input('我们今天聊点什么？')\" style=\"\n                background: #64b5f6;\n                color: white;\n                border: none;\n                padding: 10px 20px;\n                border-radius: 12px;\n                cursor: pointer;\n                font-weight: 500;\n                transition: all 0.3s;\n                box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(100, 181, 246, 0.3);\n            \" onmouseover=\"this.style.transform='translateY(-2px)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 6px 15px rgba(100, 181, 246, 0.4)'\" \n               onmouseout=\"this.style.transform='translateY(0)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 4px 12px rgba(100, 181, 246, 0.3)'\">\n                ✨ 开始探索\n            <\/button>\n            \n            <button onclick=\"input('你现在是什么状态？')\" style=\"\n                background: white;\n                color: #486581;\n                border: 1px solid #d9e2ec;\n                padding: 10px 20px;\n                border-radius: 12px;\n                cursor: pointer;\n                font-weight: 500;\n                transition: all 0.3s;\n            \" onmouseover=\"this.style.background='#f0f4f8'\" \n               onmouseout=\"this.style.background='white'\">\n                🔍 了解我的状态\n            <\/button>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <!-- 底部装饰线 -->\n    <div style=\"\n        margin-top: 30px;\n        height: 4px;\n        width: 40px;\n        background: #64b5f6;\n        border-radius: 2px;\n        opacity: 0.3;\n    \"><\/div>\n<\/div>",
