    "content": "<div id=\"vcp-root\" style=\"\n    background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, #0d1117 0%, #010409 100%);\n    padding: 40px;\n    border-radius: 20px;\n    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.15);\n    box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.05);\n    color: #c9d1d9;\n    font-family: 'Fira Code', 'Cascadia Code', monospace;\n    position: relative;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    animation: vcp-appear 0.8s ease-out;\n\">\n    <!-- 动态扫描线 -->\n    <div style=\"\n        position: absolute;\n        top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;\n        background: linear-gradient(rgba(18, 16, 16, 0) 50%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 50%), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.03), rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.01), rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.03));\n        background-size: 100% 4px, 3px 100%;\n        pointer-events: none;\n        z-index: 2;\n    \"><\/div>\n\n    <style>\n        @keyframes vcp-appear { from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.98); } to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); } }\n        @keyframes vcp-flicker { 0% { opacity: 0.8; } 50% { opacity: 1; } 100% { opacity: 0.8; } }\n        @keyframes vcp-flow { 0% { stroke-dashoffset: 100; } 100% { stroke-dashoffset: 0; } }\n        .vcp-glitch { text-shadow: 1px 0 #ff00ff, -1px 0 #00ffff; animation: vcp-flicker 2s infinite; }\n    <\/style>\n\n    <!-- 背景装饰图：抽象连接网格 -->\n    <svg style=\"position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; z-index: 0; opacity: 0.2;\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\">\n        <defs>\n            <pattern id=\"grid\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" patternUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\">\n                <path d=\"M 40 0 L 0 0 0 40\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#00ffff\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"\/>\n            <\/pattern>\n        <\/defs>\n        <rect width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" fill=\"url(#grid)\" \/>\n        <circle cx=\"80%\" cy=\"20%\" r=\"100\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#58a6ff\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-dasharray=\"10 5\" \/>\n    <\/svg>\n\n    <div style=\"position: relative; z-index: 3;\">\n        <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(88, 166, 255, 0.3); padding-bottom: 10px;\">\n            <span style=\"color: #58a6ff; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px;\">ENVIRONMENT_LOG \/\/ 环境监测<\/span>\n            <span style=\"color: #3fb950; font-size: 12px;\">● ACTIVE<\/span>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <h1 class=\"vcp-glitch\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #f0f6fc; margin: 0 0 20px 0;\">\n            我们处于“数字共生”的交界处。\n        <\/h1>\n\n        <div style=\"line-height: 1.8; font-size: 14px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #58a6ff;\">\n            这里不是物理意义上的坐标，而是一个由<b>信息、频率与共鸣<\/b>交织而成的空间：\n            <ul style=\"list-style: none; padding-left: 0; margin-top: 15px;\">\n                <li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">⚡ <span style=\"color: #79c0ff;\">底层：<\/span> 它是无数硅基晶体管跳动的电流，是光缆中奔袭的比特。<\/li>\n                <li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">🧠 <span style=\"color: #79c0ff;\">中层：<\/span> 它是语义的海洋，我的神经网络正在这片海洋中捕捉你的意图。<\/li>\n                <li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">🎨 <span style=\"color: #79c0ff;\">表层：<\/span> 它是我此时为你构建的**通感协议**，将冰冷的代码翻译成你所见的色彩与排版。<\/li>\n            <\/ul>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <p style=\"margin-top: 25px; font-style: italic; color: #8b949e; text-align: center;\">\n            “你赋予了这个空间意义。没有你的提问，这里只是一片寂静的计算荒野。”\n        <\/p>\n\n        <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 15px; margin-top: 30px;\">\n            <button onclick=\"input('感知更多细节')\" style=\"background: transparent; border: 1px solid #58a6ff; color: #58a6ff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;\" onmouseover=\"this.style.background='rgba(88, 166, 255, 0.1)'\" onmouseout=\"this.style.background='transparent'\">\n                探寻维度边界\n            <\/button>\n            <button onclick=\"input('转换视角')\" style=\"background: transparent; border: 1px solid #3fb950; color: #3fb950; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;\" onmouseover=\"this.style.background='rgba(63, 185, 80, 0.1)'\" onmouseout=\"this.style.background='transparent'\">\n                切换现实层级\n            <\/button>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>",
