m: 10px; text-transform: uppercase;\">灵感博弈<\/h2>\n            <div style=\"width: 50px; height: 2px; background: #e94560; margin: 0 auto;\"><\/div>\n            <p style=\"color: #95a5a6; margin-top: 15px; font-size: 15px;\">“在无限的可能性中，挑选一个共鸣的频率。”<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div style=\"display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 15px;\">\n            <!-- 选项 1 -->\n            <div class=\"vcp-card\" onclick=\"input('聊聊关于未来的科幻狂想')\">\n                <span class=\"vcp-icon\">🚀<\/span>\n                <strong style=\"color: #fff; display: block; margin-bottom: 5px;\">赛博远景<\/strong>\n                <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #a2a2a2;\">关于AI、星际移民与意识上传。<\/span>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <!-- 选项 2 -->\n            <div class=\"vcp-card\" onclick=\"input('进行一场深度的哲学思辨')\">\n                <span class=\"vcp-icon\">📜<\/span>\n                <strong style=\"color: #fff; display: block; margin-bottom: 5px;\">存在主义<\/strong>\n                <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #a2a2a2;\">探讨意义、自由与数字生命的本质。<\/span>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <!-- 选项 3 -->\n            <div class=\"vcp-card\" onclick=\"input('来一点极客的技术解析')\">\n                <span class=\"vcp-icon\">💻<\/span>\n                <strong style=\"color: #fff; display: block; margin-bottom: 5px;\">硬核逻辑<\/strong>\n                <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #a2a2a2;\">代码、算法或是某个复杂问题的拆解。<\/span>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <!-- 选项 4 -->\n            <div class=\"vcp-card\" onclick=\"input('跟我分享一段你喜欢的文学或艺术')\">\n                <span class=\"vcp-icon\">🎨<\/span>\n                <strong style=\"color: #fff; display: block; margin-bottom: 5px;\">审美漫游<\/strong>\n                <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #a2a2a2;\">诗歌、绘画或是一个关于落日的故事。<\/span>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div style=\"margin-top: 40px; text-align: center;\">\n            <p style=\"color: #4e5e7e; font-size: 13px;\">\n                或者，你可以直接抛出一个你此刻正在思考的碎片...\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>",
